5. 
function range(): 
args: 
1. starting number
2. ending number
3. if you want to skip numbers, eg. 1, 3, 5, 7, 9
Note that the args are positional - 1st = start, 2nd = end, 3rd = skip
if 1 arg given: arg = ending
if 2 args given: start, end
if 3: start, end, skip
example: 
range(10): 0-9
range(3, 10): 3-9
range(3, 10, 2): 3, 5, 7, 9

